    <p>Two players were arrested and charged with the crime but many people think that other players were involved. That's certainly what some social media activists allege, as they post images purportedly of those parties. One video, of a now-former player joking about the girl's condition and treatment, sparked worldwide outrage when it went viral a few weeks ago.</p>
