    <p>CATHY DAVISON: There was a tweet to a student that there was going to be attempted violence at the school. So the school made the decision to lock all the school buildings down.</p>
    <p>RUDELL: That's Cathy Davison, Steubenville's city manager. The all-clear was given a few hours later when no threat was found and things returned to normal. But there is a new normal in The Valley, as locals call the area - it's one of distrust.</p>
