    <p>UNIDENTIFIED MAN #1: I think they did a fantastic job. I was very impressed with the Algerian army. I feel sorry for anybody who's been hurt.</p>
    <p>REEVES: Another man was clearly still piecing together events.</p>
    <p>UNIDENTIFIED MAN #2: We still don't really know what's happened.</p>
    <p>UNIDENTIFIED WOMAN: Yeah.</p>
