    <p>BLOCK: Walk past the vendors hawking inaugural programs, inaugural poems, bookmarks.</p>
    <p>UNIDENTIFIED MAN #2: Bookmarkers, bookmarkers, moving forward, cheapest souvenir on the block.</p>
