    <p>In Kentucky, a push is on to remake the state's image. A couple of marketers say they're not satisfied with the state's slogan, Unbridled Spirit. They say Kentucky needs something edgier, something a little more direct. Here's Brenna Angel of member station WUKY.</p>
    <p>BRENNA ANGEL, BYLINE: The Bluegrass State is known for its horse racing...</p>
    <p>(SOUNDBITE OF HORSE RACING)</p>
